incident_updates.body: Please note the incident. Following all the necessary information. Start time: 01/06/2023 00:00 UTC Endtime: 06/06/2023 18h00 Service impact : We are in the process of renewing the Veeam licensing, but due to some issues, we entered into a Grace Period. You may experience some issues to get new licenses from our Veeam Enterprise offer, and messages speaking about Grace Period. This isn’t impacting our Managed Veeam Backup offer. Ongoing Actions: We are working the renewal with our partner, we expect to receive the new license in the following days. Root cause: : Current license entered into Grace Period.
Maintenance will begin as scheduled in 60 minutes.
